         \_doshadow\_circlet
      \_fi
      \_pdfliteral{q \_bp{\_lwidth} w \_tmp \_mv{\_bp{.5\_wd0}}{\_bp{(\_ht0-\_dp0)/2}}
                                      {\_circle{\_bp{\_dimen2}}{\_bp{\_dimen3}} B} Q}%
